Rename integration: dsc5401 -> dsc_it100

The integration was originally named for the PC5401 interface board, but
the protocol it actually implements is the DSC IT-100 superset (which is
wire-compatible with the older PC5401). Rename matches the broader scope.

- DOMAIN, manifest, service prefix, log paths: dsc5401 -> dsc_it100
- Display name: "DSC 5401" -> "DSC IT-100"
- Class prefix: DSC5401* -> DSCIT100*
- custom_components/dsc5401/ moved to custom_components/dsc_it100/
- README, hacs.json, strings, translations, services.yaml all updated
- Upstream Misterhouse DSC5401.pm attribution lines kept as-is
  (that is the upstream Perl filename, not our project name)

The top-level repo folder will be renamed separately.
